# The real Lite UI is staged here at build time (scripts/build-lite-web.sh / the
# build-lite-web-ui CI job) — index.html plus content-hashed chunks. Commit only
# placeholder.html so go:embed always has a file to compile; ignore everything
# else (including the real index.html) so multi-megabyte build output — and a
# real index.html that would make this look like a shipped UI — never land in git.
*
!.gitignore
!placeholder.html
